<h2>&nbsp;&nbsp;INTRODUCTION</h2>
<p>Technomania is a website for Punjab university students 
who by registering themselves can share innovative and fresh ideas on
various subjects, literature, sports ,lifestyle , etc. 
The articles can be viewed and commented. 
The content writer has the authority to delete any inappropriate comment. 
Posts can be arranged by categories, 
so users looking for ideas of a certain interest can find content quickly and easily.</p>
<br>

<h2>&nbsp;&nbsp;OBJECTIVES</h2>
<p>
It promotes autonomous learning by providing oppurtunities for students to
Take more control of their learning and motivates students 
To become better readers and writers. 
It creates a unique online space to represent students without spending a cart.</p>
<br>

