It offers reinforcement and feedback. 
This can drive self-esteem, personal reflection and growth, as well as confidence. 
It can be a powerful catalyst to improve literacy skills.
It provides knowledge about subjects to be able to decide 
a particular interest or aptitude for certain subjects to specialise in. 
Students will spend time reading, identifying and discussing ethics and social media.
